{
  "stem": "812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] My father died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And my 12-year-old brother had to help bury him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 19 SECONDS] [DRINKS] The Russians did the very best that they could for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "They helped me [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] to-- I went daily to a hospital that was set up for us and for the soldiers in the area.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And every day, I was taken to this hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And there, my wound was treated with a yellowish powder, which we later found out was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] penicillin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And it was a miracle how one could see that every day, the wound would get smaller and smaller.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "This hospital-- I was treated-- next-- next to me, there were amputees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "And-- and there were horrendous sights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "But I guess you learn to live with those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "And I was just very grateful that I responded to medication.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "In the interim, our heads were shaved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And that was the only way that we could rid ourselves of lice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "I know my friends-- I had a very, very dear friend Suzy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She ran away from the Russians, because she did not want her hair to be shaved.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "And I was unable to run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "I wasn't even able to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the hair was shaved, but I guess that was all of this part of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't matter at that point anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I gradually relearned to walk, gradually regained my strength.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, also, was ill with typhoid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But thank god, she recovered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was the only one who really did not take sick, who was physically well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was always scrounging and searching for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had still his knapsack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all still had our knapsacks.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
